    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "该模块主要设计服务于里程、驾驶车速及其相关得信息HMI显示，包括平均车速、目的地距离、速度预警、FDI错误上报、Gap menu、里程、PM2.5滤芯寿命显示等功能。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "该模块与其他模块得交互关系如图所示"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/SWC_OCD_DriverInfoDistance_SRC/image-2024-8-15_17-59-13.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/SWC_OCD_DriverInfoDistance_SRC/image-2024-8-15_17-59-13.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "1、AVS平均车速计算流程：from <<PIS-2085 IPC SW Specification V3.0>>    3.2.1.14.7"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "/confluence/download/attachments/4605624659/Untitled%20Diagram-1723708248405.png?version=5&modificationDate=1723717133000&api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/SWC_OCD_DriverInfoDistance_SRC/Untitled Diagram-1723708248405.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "CalcAverageSpeed → check signal valid → calculate required? → confirm scalling → Use Vehicle speed until AVS has stabilized → AVS has stabilized calculate by distance and time"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* LSB g_u32DistAccum = 1 / 64 km"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* LSB g_u32TimeAccum = 1 second"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* LSB AVS = 1/128 km/h (exponent to HMI is thus -7)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* LSB 1/128 is required to bind calculation error < 0.05 km/h"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "*"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = (g_u32DistAccum/64) / (g_u32TimeAccum/3600)                (km/h)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = (3600/64) * (g_u32DistAccum / g_u32TimeAccum)              (km/h)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = (225/4) * (g_u32DistAccum / g_u32TimeAccum)                (km/h)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = (75*3) * (g_u32DistAccum / g_u32TimeAccum), exp -2         (km/h*4)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = (75 * g_u32DistAccum / g_u32TimeAccum) * 3, exp -2         (km/h*4)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = (75 * 32 * g_u32DistAccum / g_u32TimeAccum) * 3, exp -7    (km/h*128)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "*"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* Lemma:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "*       Numerator/Denominator = (Q)uotient + (R)emainder / Denominator"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "*"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* ( g_u32DistAccum / g_u32TimeAccum ) = u32Q1 + u32R1 / g_u32TimeAccum =>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = ( 75 * 32 * ( u32Q1 + u32R1 / g_u32TimeAccum) ) * 3                       (km/h*128)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = ( 2400*u32Q1 + 32 * 75 * u32R1 / g_u32TimeAccum) ) * 3                    (km/h*128)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "*"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* ( 75 * u32R1 / g_u32TimeAccum ) = u32Q2 + u32R2 / g_u32TimeAccum =>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS =  ( 2400 * u32Q1 + 32 * u32Q2 + 32 * u32R2 / g_u32TimeAccum ) * 3       (km/h*128)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "*"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* ( 32 * u32R2 / g_u32TimeAccum ) = u32Q3 + u32R3 / g_u32TimeAccum => (ignore u32R3)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "* AVS = ( 2400 * u32Q1 + 32 * u32Q2 + u32Q3 ) * 3                              (km/h*128)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "2、Digital Speed Display << PIS-2085 IPC SW Specification V3.0>> 3.2.1.14.36"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The IPC provides a screen that shows digital speed.本模块主要用于处理不同制式下Digital Speed（例如US/Imperial: mph和Metric/Japanese:Km/h) and display in HMI or HUD(maybe not now)"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [],
      "rows": [
        [
          "digitalspeed_m.c",
          "",
          ""
        ],
        [
          "",
          "CalculteAndDisplayDigSpeedRun",
          ""
        ],
        [
          "",
          "CalcJumpToDigitalSpeed",
          "Display of the digital speed page 为什么u32VehicleSpeedDigital >P_JUMP_TO_DIGITAL_SPEED_PAGE+ 100 时返回1 ，小于P_JUMP_TO_DIGITAL_SPEED_PAGE+ 98时返回0？？ Therefore if units to present = US/English the jump will occur at 100mph and if units to present = metric, the jump will occur at 100km/h. How to understand?"
        ],
        [
          "",
          "CalcDigitalSpeed",
          "* 1. s_u16VehicleSpeedDigital is the digital speed from previous calculation represented as integer. *    Scale s_u16VehicleSpeedDigital to internal resolution: LSB = 1/2^20 (2^20 = 64*16384 = 1048576) * 2. Depending on selected unit scale VehicleSpeedFiltered to resolution 1/2^20. *     2b. If Metric: Scale by 16384 *     2c. If US/Imperial: Scale by 10181 (10181/16384 ~= 0.6214 * 3. Calculate Fractional part of VehicleSPeedFiltered: *    u32VehicleSpeedFiltered_tmp = u32Integer + u32Fraction * 4. Check fractional part against the calibrations. If True, add \"+1\" to the integer part (scaled) * 5. Divide integer part by 2^20. The result is the new digital speed."
        ]
      ]
    },
